but she was rude.

346
00:15:41.250 --> 00:15:43.060
She--

347
00:15:43.160 --> 00:15:46.230
she called me a loser.
and I just--

348
00:15:49.280 --> 00:15:51.240
I went nuts.

349
00:15:54.170 --> 00:15:56.940
Alan Ross. the defendant
