00:22:33.950 --> 00:22:36.510
what this means
in layman's terms?

522
00:22:36.580 --> 00:22:39.850
That Alan Ross's DNA was
found on Angela Cole's body.

523
00:22:39.950 --> 00:22:42.120
The odds of that DNA
belonging to someone else

524
00:22:42.160 --> 00:22:43.820
is pretty much zero.

525
00:22:43.860 --> 00:22:45.030
Thank you.

526
00:22:48.200 --> 00:22:51.800
There is nothing illegal
about building a shrine.

527
00:22:51.830 --> 00:22:53.300
Correct.

528
00:22:53.430 --> 00:22:55.340
And the fact that
a man's DNA is present

529
00:22:55.370 --> 00:22:58.970
on a dead woman's body doesn't
mean that person killed her.

530
00:22:59.010 --> 00:23:00.540
because there are lots of ways

531
00:23:00.610 --> 00:23:03.340
