or kisses her.

534
00:23:07.680 --> 00:23:09.050
Correct.

535
00:23:09.120 --> 00:23:12.340
So the fact that Mr. Ross's
DNA is on Angela Cole

536
00:23:12.370 --> 00:23:13.890
doesn't mean a damn thing.

537
00:23:13.950 --> 00:23:17.760
In fact. there were six other
different DNA samples

538
00:23:17.830 --> 00:23:19.220
