541
00:23:22.560 --> 00:23:24.230
people who were
at the birthday party.

542
00:23:24.330 --> 00:23:26.830
But the fact remains.
there were six other

543
00:23:26.870 --> 00:23:29.400
DNA samples found on her body.

544
00:23:30.540 --> 00:23:31.740
Correct.

545
00:23:33.170 --> 00:23:35.970
Nothing further.

546
00:23:36.040 --> 00:23:37.640
Mr. Price?

