728
00:31:39.220 --> 00:31:42.150
Punched her repeatedly.

729
00:31:42.220 --> 00:31:43.530
It was two years ago.

730
00:31:43.660 --> 00:31:46.220
She needed stitches
to stop the bleeding.

731
00:31:46.360 --> 00:31:48.570
Correct?
