732
00:31:48.700 --> 00:31:50.570
She had a fractured
orbital bone.

733
00:31:50.670 --> 00:31:52.870
Like I said.
it was a while ago.

734
00:31:52.970 --> 00:31:55.240
OK.

735
00:31:55.380 --> 00:31:57.670
Let's talk about
