through a window.

742
00:32:11.660 --> 00:32:13.190
Yes.

743
00:32:13.230 --> 00:32:16.100
Defense exhibit K.

744
00:32:16.160 --> 00:32:17.710
This took place

745
00:32:17.750 --> 00:32:19.880
