747
00:32:26.440 --> 00:32:29.400
That is you. correct?

748
00:32:29.430 --> 00:32:33.180
Yes. it's not exactly
my finest moment.

749
00:32:33.210 --> 00:32:36.150
Certainly not
your worst either.

750
00:32:36.220 --> 00:32:38.050
Defense Exhibit L.

751
00:32:38.120 --> 00:32:41.760
Mr. White.
that is you on 15th Street.

752
00:32:41.860 --> 00:32:44.070
