776
00:33:36.300 --> 00:33:39.280
I--I still get angry.

777
00:33:39.310 --> 00:33:41.800
It--it just happens sometimes.

778
00:33:41.830 --> 00:33:44.510
It just happens. like
when you beat Angela the day

779
00:33:44.640 --> 00:33:46.820
